  "content": {
    "visible_text": "Community Partners Thank you to all our community partners, students, family members and volunteers who have donated time, talent, services, goods, and financial contributions in support of the Quantum Community Dojo. The generosity of our volunteer community makes our work possible, and every cent is put to good use furthering our mission of making martial arts training accessible to all! Artists: Jude LeTronik 2020 Adult T-shirt design. Andi Plantenberg Youth t-shirt design 2020 and campaign materials. Amber Yada Youth t-shirt design 2019. Eunice Moyle Youth t-shirt design 2018 and marketing materials. Event Donors: Canela Bistro & Wine Bar Hosted The Quantum Leap 2017, 2018, 2019. DJ André Lucero Live DJ set for The Quantum Leap 2017, 2018, 2019. Marcus Shelby Live jazz performance for The Quantum Leap 2018. Whole Wine Wine donations for The Quantum Leap 2017, 2018, 2019. Rainbow Grocery Fort Point Beer Co. Dandelion Chocolate Mama Lamees Barebottle Brewing Co. Terra Firma Farm In-kind Donors: Capitol Light Light and fan donation and installation for the Dojo, 2018. Fiscal Donors: 2B Living Greybrick Partners Homelight Reviews Facebook Community Dojo Quantum Martial Arts is a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit in the State of California, and we thrive on the generosity of people like you. All donations are tax-deductible. Quantum’s tax ID number is 26-1534597. No donation is too small, or too large. Whether it’s $20 or $20,000, every cent will be hugely appreciated and put to good use. Support Our Kids Donate now to support our youth scholarship program which allows families in need to train at reduced cost. We believe investment in our community involves investing in our youth. Our Sister Schools Our Seattle Dojo has served thousands of students since opening on Capitol Hill in 1995, and currently offers youth and adult classes in the Central District. Our Portland Dojo was established in 2020, and currently offers youth and adult classes in Southeast Portland. A WordPress.com Website .",
